<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>I am fire<br />
Burn those who dare to care for me<br />
And my fuel are memories, fuel are memories of you<br />
They perish with the heat, perish with the heat<br />
So I can move on<br />
Flower of iron<br />
Shrivelled up to hide the imposter in me<br />
“Hey, why did you leave? Why did you leave?”<br />
Don’t let those words out of me<br />
Imposter’s about to speak<br />
So I chewed on Huameitang</p>
</div>

